'''Kep''' was the unit of measurement [[Adumari]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] used in flight speed instead of the [[The galaxy/Legends|galactic]] standard [[Kilometer/Legends|klicks]]. They also use the [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]] [[Standard hour|hour]] instead of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] hour.

Its origins lie on the exact thousand paces measured by the stride of some long-dead [[Cartann]] [[perator]]. The Adumari measurement was about eighty percent of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] standard.

